---
// Events section component
---

<section class="services" id="events">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Reunion Events</h2>
      <p>Join us for a weekend full of memories, laughter, and reconnection. We've planned exciting events to celebrate our 30th reunion and catch up with old friends.</p>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">RSVP FOR EVENTS</a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">🎓</div>
        <h3>School Tour</h3>
        <p>Saturday, September 5th • 9:00 AM - 11:00 AM<br>Take a guided tour of Lincoln East High School. See how our alma mater has changed and reminisce about our high school days.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">🥂</div>
        <h3>Sunday Social</h3>
        <p>Sunday, September 6th • 7:00 PM<br>Join us at South Apothecary Loft to reconnect with classmates and celebrate our reunion.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="membership-section">
      <div class="membership-content">
        <h2>Reunion Pricing</h2>
        <p>Early bird pricing available until March 1st, 2026. All events include food, drinks, and entertainment. Family members welcome at additional cost.</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">VIEW PRICING</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mixers-section">
      <div class="mixers-content">
        <h2>Hotel Accommodations</h2>
        <p>Special group rates available at The Cornhusker Marriott. Book your room by April 1st, 2026 to secure the reunion rate. Shuttle service provided to all events.</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary">BOOK HOTEL</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .services {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: #f8f9fa;
  }
  
  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }
  
  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }
  
  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: 42px;
    color: #1e40af;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  
  .section-header p {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #666;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 30px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
    gap: 30px;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }
  
  .service-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 40px 30px;
    border-radius: 15px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .service-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  }
  
  .service-icon {
    font-size: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  
  .service-card h3 {
    font-size: 24px;
    color: #1e40af;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  
  .service-card p {
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 16px;
  }
  
  .membership-section,
  .mixers-section {
    background: white;
    padding: 60px 40px;
    border-radius: 15px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }
  
  .membership-section h2,
  .mixers-section h2 {
    font-size: 36px;
    color: #1e40af;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  
  .membership-section p,
  .mixers-section p {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #666;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 30px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .btn {
    padding: 16px 32px;
    border-radius: 30px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 16px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  
  .btn-primary {
    background: #1e40af;
    color: white;
    border: 2px solid #1e40af;
  }
  
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #1e3a8b;
    border-color: #1e3a8b;
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.3);
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: 32px;
    }
    
    .membership-section h2,
    .mixers-section h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
    }
  }
</style>
